Mobile-P2kMoto

This module uses the p2kmoto library to interface with Motorola Mobile
phones using an USB cable.  It allows access to the filesystem as well
as accessing the SEEM record.

=========================

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module is a wrapper around the p2kmoto library
(http://moto4lin.sourceforge.net/). It is known to work under
Linux. The library works under Windows as well, but the module has not
been tested there.

